{"tid":2236273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又亂放生]公司認管有虛假「加衛苗」女董事獲撤控　官促三思撤控決定︰假疫苗一支都嫌多","createTime":"2020-10-09T10:51:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T13:00:37.000Z","uid":51271,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"635eaf481e6d70fa37c0ffd84c2f735a43e198a6","tid":2236273,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T10:51:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20201009/s00001/1602237833144/%e5%85%ac%e5%8f%b8%e8%aa%8d%e7%ae%a1%e6%9c%89%e8%99%9b%e5%81%87%e3%80%8c%e5%8a%a0%e8%a1%9b%e8%8b%97%e3%80%8d%e5%a5%b3%e8%91%a3%e4%ba%8b%e7%8d%b2%e6%92%a4%e6%8e%a7-%e5%ae%98%e4%bf%83%e4%b8%89%e6%80%9d%e6%92%a4%e6%8e%a7%e6%b1%ba%e5%ae%9a-%e5%81%87%e7%96%ab%e8%8b%97%e4%b8%80%e6%94%af%e9%83%bd%e5%ab%8c%e5%a4%9a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20201009%2Fs00001%2F1602237833144%2F%25e5%2585%25ac%25e5%258f%25b8%25e8%25aa%258d%25e7%25ae%25a1%25e6%259c%2589%25e8%2599%259b%25e5%2581%2587%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%258a%25a0%25e8%25a1%259b%25e8%258b%2597%25e3%2580%258d%25e5%25a5%25b3%25e8%2591%25a3%25e4%25ba%258b%25e7%258d%25b2%25e6%2592%25a4%25e6%258e%25a7-%25e5%25ae%2598%25e4%25bf%2583%25e4%25b8%2589%25e6%2580%259d%25e6%2592%25a4%25e6%258e%25a7%25e6%25b1%25ba%25e5%25ae%259a-%25e5%2581%2587%25e7%2596%25ab%25e8%258b%2597%25e4%25b8%2580%25e6%2594%25af%25e9%2583%25bd%25e5%25ab%258c%25e5%25a4%259a&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzpggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=87be6cf2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20201009%2Fs00001%2F1602237833144%2F%25e5%2585%25ac%25e5%258f%25b8%25e8%25aa%258d%25e7%25ae%25a1%25e6%259c%2589%25e8%2599%259b%25e5%2581%2587%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%258a%25a0%25e8%25a1%259b%25e8%258b%2597%25e3%2580%258d%25e5%25a5%25b3%25e8%2591%25a3%25e4%25ba%258b%25e7%258d%25b2%25e6%2592%25a4%25e6%258e%25a7-%25e5%25ae%2598%25e4%25bf%2583%25e4%25b8%2589%25e6%2580%259d%25e6%2592%25a4%25e6%258e%25a7%25e6%25b1%25ba%25e5%25ae%259a-%25e5%2581%2587%25e7%2596%25ab%25e8%258b%2597%25e4%25b8%2580%25e6%2594%25af%25e9%2583%25bd%25e5%25ab%258c%25e5%25a4%259a&h=42c75036\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20201009/s00001/1602237833144/%e5%85%ac%e5%8f%b8%e8%aa%8d%e7%ae%a1%e6%9c%89%e8%99%9b%e5%81%87%e3%80%8c%e5%8a%a0%e8%a1%9b%e8%8b%97%e3%80%8d%e5%a5%b3%e8%91%a3%e4%ba%8b%e7%8d%b2%e6%92%a4%e6%8e%a7-%e5%ae%98%e4%bf%83%e4%b8%89%e6%80%9d%e6%92%a4%e6%8e%a7%e6%b1%ba%e5%ae%9a-%e5%81%87%e7%96%ab%e8%8b%97%e4%b8%80%e6%94%af%e9%83%bd%e5%ab%8c%e5%a4%9a</a><br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣一間醫療公司涉管有防範HPV病毒的虛假「加衛苗」（Gardasil），公司及一名董事被檢控。案件今（9日）在東區裁判法院提訊，公司雖認罪，惟律政司決定撤銷董事控罪，裁判官質疑，稱案情嚴重，「假疫苗一支都嫌多」，促律政司再三考慮撤控決定。案件押後至11月13日，待控方再草擬提出撤控的陳辭。<br />\n<br />\n兩名被告分別為「港健醫療集團有限公司 」（MEDHK GROUP LTD）及其公司女員工張維瑄（55歲），她報稱任公司董事。兩者分別被控一項「管有已應用虛假商品說明的貨品作售賣或任何商業或製造用途」罪，港健醫療認罪；張維瑄則獲控方提出撤控。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>主任裁判官錢禮質疑，案件嚴重，並涉及重大公共衛生問題，雖然辯方稱涉案假疫苗數量少，但錢官說「假疫苗一支都嫌多」，先押後案件至11月13日，着控方作進一步陳辭，解釋為何撤銷張維瑄控罪。</strong><br />\n<br />\n港健醫療承認的案情指出，衛生署及海關今年7月展開聯合行動，搜查港健醫療位於銅鑼灣廣場2期19樓辦公室，發現6支虛假的「9合1加衛苗疫苗」，疫苗虛假地說明由藥廠「MSD」製造，卻非實情，經檢驗後更發現假疫苗比起正貨缺少部分化學物，或可引致嚴重後果甚至死亡。"},{"pid":"93996c9ad40c28a36c5b51c9c7496e17f7efabe6","tid":2236273,"uid":92064,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T10:53:31.000Z","msg":"大波華收左幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"231dfe97c6c0138023352736c793fff2c79756b5","tid":2236273,"uid":20170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T10:54:14.000Z","msg":"有險可守<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b292b00bd083a9781df2bce2d514e31610ebb589","tid":2236273,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T10:54:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse